name: Spider Murphy
description: Arabella,going by the nickname ofSpider Murphy, is a skillednetrunnerin theCyberpunkuniverse. Spider Murphy metRache Bartmossfor the first time after overhearing her Corporate father had wiped his SIN from the system.
